hot reload =>> is immediate change happens after changing the UI, apply changes in build method  in no time

when u change anything if the UI code,   dart highlight this part as a "dirty"    then look for the nearest "build" method from this change,   then rerun this build() method again

لما بتغير حاجه في جزء ال UI
دارت  بيعلم علي الجزء دا كـ dirty
وبعدين بيدور علي اقرب build  للجزء  اللي متغير دا 
وبعدين يشغل الجزء دا بس     rerun build method
